Popular On Air Personality, Nedu Wazobia has said that female Big Brother Naija housemates participate in the reality show to make themselves available for ‘customers’. Nedu made this known during his podcast show. He said some of the ladies only have vagina to offer. “The reason why many go to BBN is that they are hungry. Do you know what Big Brother does for you? It takes you from the low and shoots you up but there is no substance to hold you. ”It is vagina most of them have to offer. They intentionally go there just to get customers,” he stated. Nedu had in his podcast said a friend asked him for the contact of one of the BBN female housemates and he gave her N3 million just to speak to her. ”My guy is a giver, the day he had sex with her he gave her almost $15, 000.”